Dialogue: 0,00:02:55.45,00:03:00.79,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}指引着我  前往远方
Dialogue: 0,00:03:01.00,00:03:09.17,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一路披荆斩棘  杀出血路
Dialogue: 0,00:03:11.42,00:03:14.34,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Yo guess who’s back Everybody get down
