Dialogue: 0,00:03:27.90,00:03:32.24,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}被命运捉弄  I’m falling down
Dialogue: 0,00:03:32.53,00:03:37.66,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你同奏的和声  再也不会响起
Dialogue: 0,00:03:37.70,00:03:42.83,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你强烈的香气还在心头萦绕
Dialogue: 0,00:03:43.62,00:03:45.96,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不愿再继续等待
Dialogue: 0,00:03:47.46,00:03:49.21,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hey guess who’s back
